{"tid":2341752,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"條女幫我含含下，無啦啦流眼淚","createTime":"2020-12-26T15:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T15:22:14.000Z","uid":31447,"like":5,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7adaf9b843886c269333e37aa01528bed9e278b6","tid":2341752,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:09:55.000Z","msg":"其實今日晏晝佢都有啲唔開心㗎啦<br />\n食完飯捉佢黎扑野，佢係有少少唔願意<br />\n就喺度吹吹下蕭嘅時候，無啦啦望住我留咗兩滴眼淚<br />\n我個心即刻痛左一痛<br />\n即刻問佢咩事<br />\n原來佢含得太深喉頂到個喉嚨定，先唔覺意標左兩滴眼淚<br />\n大家冰釋前嫌之後，就繼續扑野"},{"pid":"410d40a81ec74c7970d43f182cdcc65b5c199f99","tid":2341752,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"禁室虐待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲放返人哋出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf99919dc6082bc53547d28ac083f1cd3eb9f83","tid":2341752,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"410d40a81ec74c7970d43f182cdcc65b5c199f99","tid":2341752,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"禁室虐待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲放返人哋出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:12:50.000Z","msg":"佢自願俾我鎖的"},{"pid":"4319695ec3d7ca2c041c6ff29b48e98ab9bbc0d3","tid":2341752,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:13:00.000Z","msg":"樓主非法禁錮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f333d9234fddec542d5a85b95ed4bb3ef59a944","tid":2341752,"uid":369015,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T15:13:07.000Z","msg":"應該係細個對牙籤有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後你碌鳩trigger到"},{"pid":"137929bfbd7b8634346f1973ccff452b9ebcb2a8","tid":2341752,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4319695ec3d7ca2c041c6ff29b48e98ab9bbc0d3","tid":2341752,"uid":3890